title: The 500 AWHP, AWD, Hillclimbing, Psycho Syclone - /TUNED
description: We end our fourth season with probably our favorite subject car of all time, Adam Auerbach's GMC Syclone Hillclimber. This truck is what "Tuned" is all about; customized in every way possible, 100% function with form following suit. It's nasty, dirty, evil, and perfect.
